# U-Download

Fast, cross-platform YouTube downloader with beautiful GUI interface.

## Features

- **Zero Dependencies**: All required tools (yt-dlp, aria2c, ffmpeg) are bundled - no separate installation needed
- **High-Speed Downloads**: Uses aria2c for multi-connection downloading
- **Format Selection**: Download video, audio, or both in various quality options
- **Video Trimming**: Built-in video trimming with precise time controls
- **Cross-Platform**: Works on Windows, macOS, and Linux
- **Beautiful GUI**: Modern, intuitive interface built with Tauri and React
- **Progress Tracking**: Real-time download progress with detailed information
- **System Notifications**: Get notified when downloads complete

## Installation

This Chocolatey package installs U-Download with all dependencies bundled. No additional software installation required.

## Usage

After installation, run `u-download` from command line or find "U-Download" in your Start Menu.

## What's Included

- U-Download application
- Bundled yt-dlp (latest version)
- Bundled aria2c for fast downloads  
- Bundled FFmpeg for video processing
- Desktop shortcuts and Start Menu entries

## Zero Setup Required

Unlike other YouTube downloaders, U-Download comes with everything needed to work immediately. No need to:
- Install Python
- Install yt-dlp separately
- Install aria2c
- Install FFmpeg
- Configure paths or dependencies

Just install and use!
